# ==============================================================================
# Final_Scripts GitHub / Code Ocean Ignore Rules
# ==============================================================================
#
# This .gitignore belongs to the nested Git repository rooted at:
#
#   Scripts_2025/Final_Scripts/
#
# It is the file shown in GitHub Desktop in the screenshot. The broader
# project-level allowlist lives one directory tree above this nested repo:
#
#   ../../.gitignore
#
# Use this nested repo only if you are uploading the cleaned numbered source
# pipeline by itself. For the full reviewer capsule, build a clean staging repo
# from the project root so it can also include `reproducible_workflow/`, `docs/`,
# frozen final figures/tables, and the root `./run` entry point.
# ==============================================================================

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local/editor/session state.
# These files are machine-specific and should never be part of a reproducibility
# capsule.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# macOS metadata
.DS_Store

# R session artefacts
.Rhistory
.RData
.Rproj.user/

# Editor backup files
*.bak

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local environments and developer tooling.
# The analysis scripts declare package requirements; local virtual environments
# and IDE/copilot metadata should not be uploaded.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Python virtual environment (used only by VS Code tooling, not analysis code)
.venv/
.github/copilot-instructions.md

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Archived, exploratory, and scratch source folders.
# Only the numbered scripts, command-line runners, helpers, and reviewer-facing
# documentation at this repo root should be tracked.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Other/
Tmp/
figures/
Scripts prior to rerunning ML model/
For targetted panel MS/

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Generated run logs and local input reports.
# These are regenerated by the command-line wrappers and are intentionally local.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

pipeline_logs/20260617_144955/run_manifest.tsv
/pipeline_logs
/clean_pipeline/logs
local_input_check_report.tsv
/output_comparison_4_1_examples

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Generated manuscript output trees.
# These are useful locally but should not be committed from this nested repo.
# The full Code Ocean capsule should regenerate/stage outputs through the
# project-root workflow.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

/outputs
/final_manuscript_objects
/manuscript_writing

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Archive policy.
# Most archive content is intentionally excluded. The support-analysis subfolder
# is retained because it contains reviewer-relevant audit/support material.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

/archive/*
!/archive/support_analysis/
!/archive/support_analysis/**

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Agent/runtime instruction files.
# Keep local agent instructions out of the public source-pipeline repo unless
# deliberately reviewed for publication.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

AGENTS.md
